OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDyfed-Powys Police chief   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcalls for fresh drugs      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fapproach                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Drug-related deaths in Wales "will     
OL,6, continue to rise" unless a different   
OL,7, approach is taken, according to        
OL,8, Dyfed-Powys Police's chief constable.  
OL,10,FRichard Lewis said he believed drug use
OL,11,Fshould be seen as a public health issue
OL,12,Frather than a criminal justice problem.
OL,14,FHe said evidence around                
OL,15,Fdecriminalisation of drugs should be   
OL,16,Ftaken from other countries, but        
OL,17,Fadmitted it was a "political matter".  
OL,19,FThe Home Office has been asked to      
OL,20,Fcomment.                               
